recipe.build:
sed -r '/abi \{/,/}/ s/enable true/enable false/' -i app/build.gradle
./gradlew assembleLibreRelease
mv app/build/outputs/apk/libre/release/app-libre-release-unsigned.apk /outputs/unsigned.apk
